        <!-- homepage body - right column -->
        <div id="home-body-right-col">
          <h2 class="title" id="page-title">Beer Canada members represent over 90% of all domestic beer sold in Canada and $14 billion a year in economic activity</h2>                                        <div id="user-content">
              <div class="region region-content">
    <div id="block-system-main" class="block block-system">

    
  <div class="content">
    <div id="node-28" class="node node-homepage">

      
  
  <div class="content">
    <div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><p>Beer Canada is the national voice of beer, representing over 35¬†Canadian brewing companies that account for 90% of beer made in Canada and a category that supports 163,200 Canadian jobs, $14 billion in real gross domestic product and $5.8 billion in tax revenues for federal, provincial and municipal levels of government.</p>
</div></div></div>  </div>

  
  
</div>
  </div>
</div>
  </div>
          </div>
